link_desc:
Unofficial template for radio intelbras APC 5A-20, designed for the latest firmware 7.65 (at this date). It's based on generic Linux template with custom OIDs and triggers.

It has a custom "aplication" named RF and currently display the following information:

  • Frequency (MHz)
  • Channel Bandwidth (MHz)
  • Transmission Power (dBm)
  • Country Code
  • Wireless Protocol (80211x or IPOLL)
  • Mac Address

It has a custom Trigger to warn when a radio is configured to operate in the maximum power, you can disable it if you want.
author: Benjamim Gois
